    <h3>More from LepBase...</h3>
    <p>We aim to provide a comparative genomics resource for the Lepidotera research 
      community, of which this ensembl instance is only the beginning, visit 
      <a href="http://lepbase.org" title="lepbase.org">lepbase.org</a> to find out more about the project.
