  <p>This is the first release of the LepBase ensembl genome browser, building upon the 
    Lepidopteran content already available through <a href="http://metazoa.ensembl.org" 
    title="metazoa.ensembl.org">Ensembl Metazoa</a> to deliver the datasets and analyses 
    of most value to the Lepidoptera community.  If there is something missing that you 
    would like to see then please <a href="mailto:contact@lepbase.org" 
    title="contact@lepbase.org">contact us</a>. 
  </p>
